00:41:30.562 --> 00:41:32.270
right all the time,
and it's transparent,

00:41:32.270 --> 00:41:35.600
and we don't notice it
unless it's not there.

00:41:35.600 --> 00:41:38.300
Why or why isn't
changing people's minds

00:41:38.300 --> 00:41:42.500
about that particular
thing sort of part

00:41:42.500 --> 00:41:44.300
of the solution
where people might

00:41:44.300 --> 00:41:47.600
stop hoarding their money, and
then spending it privately,

00:41:47.600 --> 00:41:49.351
and support higher tax
rates, for example?

